englishquestion:
Determine whether the water pump requires maintenance. The following factors need to be considered:  
1. The current status of the water pump;  
2. Whether the usage duration of the pump has exceeded the recommended maintenance interval (assumed to be 1000 hours);  
3. Whether the water pump is under warranty;  
4. Whether the time since the last maintenance exceeds the recommended maintenance interval (assumed to be 6 months).
